snippet.title: World Stadium EX (PS1) - Gameplay
snippet.description:
A full game of World Stadium EX. The game has real licensed NPB teams, but I chose to play with two fictional teams, the World Stars vs. the Errors. Stay for the wild finish. 

"T-t-t-t-tell me why..."
